A Colenso man was brutally gunned down along Colenso main street, earlier this evening, 18 October. It is believed that the man had just purchased an item at the local shop, when he was shot dead.At this stage the motive of the killing is unknown. Colenso police and Ladysmith forensic teams have closed off the area, to gather much needed evidence from the scene. Colenso police will conduct an investigation into the murder.The man has not been identified yet